          "zh": "Heavyweight Hoodie Manufacturing | Oversized T-Shirt Production",
          "en": "Heavyweight Hoodie Manufacturing | Oversized T-Shirt Production"
        },
        "content": {
          "zh": "Premium Heavyweight Hoodie Manufacturing Services://\nAt Kellogg Fashion, we specialize in producing premium heavyweight hoodies for streetwear brands worldwide. Our hoodies are crafted with 400–600gsm high-quality fabrics to ensure durability, comfort, and a perfect oversized fit. We combine modern streetwear design with precise garment construction, helping brands deliver consistent, trend-driven products to their customers.//\nWhy Choose Kellogg for Heavyweight Hoodies://\nExpertise in Heavyweight Fabrics: We work with cotton fleece, French terry, brushed fleece, and custom fabric blends designed to maintain shape, softness, and color after multiple washes.//\nPrecision Sewing & Construction:Double-needle stitching, reinforced shoulder taping, rib attachment, and flatlock seams ensure durability and premium hand-feel.//\nCustom Design & Fit:Oversized silhouettes, drop shoulders, kangaroo pockets, and adjustable hoods are all tailored to your brand specifications.//\nFlexible Production & MOQ:From small-batch startup collections to large-scale orders, we maintain consistent quality and timely delivery.",
          "en": "Premium Heavyweight Hoodie Manufacturing Services://\nAt Kellogg Fashion, we specialize in producing premium heavyweight hoodies for streetwear brands worldwide. Our hoodies are crafted with 400–600gsm high-quality fabrics to ensure durability, comfort, and a perfect oversized fit. We combine modern streetwear design with precise garment construction, helping brands deliver consistent, trend-driven products to their customers.//\nWhy Choose Kellogg for Heavyweight Hoodies://\nExpertise in Heavyweight Fabrics: We work with cotton fleece, French terry, brushed fleece, and custom fabric blends designed to maintain shape, softness, and color after multiple washes.//\nPrecision Sewing & Construction:Double-needle stitching, reinforced shoulder taping, rib attachment, and flatlock seams ensure durability and premium hand-feel.//\nCustom Design & Fit:Oversized silhouettes, drop shoulders, kangaroo pockets, and adjustable hoods are all tailored to your brand specifications.//\nFlexible Production & MOQ:From small-batch startup collections to large-scale orders, we maintain consistent quality and timely delivery."
        },
